Plague Doctor (24)

You can spread plague to one card each night. Players won't know which of their cards have plague. Active spread (AS): You spread plague yourself per night. Passive spread (PS): Any card who actively visits you (except own) gets the plague. Fast spread (FS): Any card having plague will spread plague if it visits or gets visited. This can also be spread in self-cards. Your team will win if every enemy card gets the plague and will flee the game as winner. However if plague completes its spread at night, then the next day will be the players' only chance to find and vote out the plague doctor to survive. You cannot be killed by the werewolves. Aura: Unknown Ability: Active (in AS) and Passive (in PS and FS)
